import { Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom"
import { ListGame } from "./listGame"
import { ListCategory } from "./listCategory"
import { AddCategore } from "./addCtegory"
import { Login } from "./login"
import { Sal } from "./sal"
import { MoreDetailes } from "./moreDetailes"
import { SignIn } from "./sighIn"
import { HomePage } from "./homePage"

export const Routing = () => {
    return <Routes>
        <Route path="liG" element={<ListGame></ListGame>}></Route>
        <Route path="liC" element={<ListCategory></ListCategory>}></Route>
        <Route path="addC" element={<AddCategore></AddCategore>}></Route>
        <Route path="Login" element={<Login></Login>}></Route>
        <Route path="sal" element={<Sal></Sal>}></Route>
        <Route path="Mdetaile/:img" element={<MoreDetailes></MoreDetailes>}></Route>
        <Route path="sign" element={<SignIn></SignIn>}></Route>
        <Route path="homeP" element={<HomePage></HomePage>}></Route>
    </Routes>
}
